This session burned ~25 minutes on schema/auth/log-channel mismatches:
- `task` vs `label` column on `operations` table
- `/metrics` returning 401 (auth was added in v2.45.21, forgotten)
- `manager.send_line` writing to `operation_log` table + WS, not container stdout
